We have thermometers too, just didn&#39;t mention them.   I will grab a compass and some motion detectors.   Must say I didn&#39;t even think of grabbing a hygrometer but will definitely look into it.  The trifield meter is a bit out of budget right now but we are going to get one here soon. And yes we do have a K2 meter already.   We have most everything I could think of, just looking for some oddities.  One of the things I found a while ago was a homemade battery detector.  Basically it was 4 batteries running 2 led&#39;s that somebody had made.  It was used to correlate the draining of equipment batteries.  Wish I could find it again.  That&#39;s the type of stuff I&#39;m looking for, stuff that someone made that helped them out.

